ygData.msgSnippet: Sinochaie s Partisan for primary and Smoldering brand in secondary. 2 electrum black sapphire earrings (ac2 35hp, under 1k for a pair). 2 velium fire opal
ygData.messageBody:
Sinochaie's Partisan for primary and Smoldering brand in secondary.
2 electrum black sapphire earrings (ac2 35hp, under 1k for a pair).
2 velium fire opal rings (ac6 65hp, 1k for a pair).
Ry'Gorr chain collar (ac9 4str 4sta) for neck.
Bone mask of the Jarsath for face.
Crown of the Froglock Kings for head.
FBSS for waist.
Spider fur cloak for back.

This is considering you do sell them for 18k or so heh.
